        "label": "Lexical structure",
        "href": "../guide/lexical.html"
      }
    ]
  },
  "L006": {
    "title": "Unterminated block comment",
    "canonicalMessage": "unterminated block comment",
    "cause": [
      "A block comment beginning with /* reached the end of the source without a closing */ delimiter.",
      "Block comments do not nest. The lexer consumes the remainder of the source as comment text before reporting the error."
    ],
    "example": "/* review this definition\nconst Int threshold = 5;",
    "exampleLanguage": "alam",
    "remedy": [
      "Add the closing */ delimiter.",
      "When commenting out source that already contains a block comment, use line comments instead because ALAM block comments do not nest."
    ],
    "related": [
      {
        "label": "Lexical structure",
        "href": "../guide/lexical.html",
        "group": "Model"
      }
    ]
  },
  "L007": {
    "title": "Stray ampersand",
    "canonicalMessage": "stray '&'; the conjunction operator is '&&'",
    "cause": [
      "The lexer encountered one ampersand not followed by another ampersand.",
      "ALAM defines logical conjunction as && only. It has no bitwise ampersand operator."
    ],
    "example": "const Bool result = true & false;",
    "exampleLanguage": "alam",
    "remedy": [
      "Replace the lone ampersand with && when logical conjunction is intended.",
      "Remove the operator when no conjunction was intended."
    ],
    "related": [
      {
        "label": "Bool",
        "href": "../type/Bool.html",
        "group": "Entity"
      },
      {
        "label": "Lexical structure",
        "href": "../guide/lexical.html",
        "group": "Model"
      }
    ]
  },
  "L008": {
    "title": "Stray vertical bar",
    "canonicalMessage": "stray '|'; the disjunction operator is '||'",
    "cause": [
      "The lexer encountered one vertical bar not followed by another vertical bar.",
      "ALAM defines logical disjunction as || only. It has no bitwise vertical-bar operator."
    ],
    "example": "const Bool result = true | false;",
    "exampleLanguage": "alam",
    "remedy": [
      "Replace the lone vertical bar with || when logical disjunction is intended.",
      "Remove the operator when no disjunction was intended."
    ],
    "related": [
